data.description: Charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath home nestled in a fantastic location! Situated right across the street from the neighborhood pool and conveniently near major highways. This lovely home boasts fresh upgrades, including recently replaced carpet, LVP flooring, and fresh paint throughout. Inside, you'll find a generously sized living room adorned with a brick fireplace, while the kitchen features an inviting island and a gas range for your culinary delights. Enjoy a bright primary suite featuring a jetted tub, dual sinks, and a spacious walk-in closet. Ample storage with linen closets, walk-in closets in two of the three bedrooms, and an additional 5x5 storage area available in the garage. Roof and windows recently replaced.
